column1:
Magento Store Locator extension allows locating stores and getting directions with Google Map integrated:
1. To add/ import stores with location, time schedule and other information, go to Store Locator -> Manage Stores.
2. To set days off for store(s), go to Store Locator -> Manage Holidays.
3. To set days with special working time for store(s), go to Store Locator -> Manage Special Days.
4. To configure Store Locator extension, go to Store Locator -> Settings.
column2:
Magento Store Locator extension allows locating stores and getting directions with Google Map integrated:
1. To add/ import stores with location, time schedule and other information, go to Store Locator -> Manage Stores.
2. To set days off for store(s), go to Store Locator -> Manage Holidays.
3. To set days with special working time for store(s), go to Store Locator -> Manage Special Days.
4. To configure Store Locator extension, go to Store Locator -> Settings.
